{
  "text": "Mouse monoclonal anti-FLAG M2 antibody was obtained from Sigma, and rat monoclonal anti-HA (clone 3F10) antibody was obtained from Roche. Rabbit antibodies recognizing phospho-AMPK\u2423 (Thr-172), AMPK\u2423, and COX IV were obtained from Cell Signaling Technology. Mouse anti-GAPDH monoclonal antibody was obtained from Novus Biologicals. HRPconjugated rabbit polyclonal anti-tubulin antibody was obtained from Abcam. Rabbit polyclonal antibody used to detect endogenous CTRP9 was generated previously [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "205364087"
